  &lt;h2 align=&#34;center&#34;&gt;Level-Set Visualizer&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div align=&#34;center&#34;&gt;
    Visualize image segmentation based on level set method.
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

